import React from "react"
import Navbar from 'react-bootstrap/Navbar'
import { Nav,FormControl,Button,Form} from "react-bootstrap"
const NavigationBar = () => {
    let navItems = ["home","news","events","agenda","music","biography","rental catalogue","order","contact"]
    const NavList = () => {navItems.map(item => {
        return <Nav.Link href="#home">{item}</Nav.Link>
    })}
    return (<>
        <Navbar bg="dark" variant="dark">
          <Navbar.Brand href="#home">JDM |</Navbar.Brand>
          <Nav className="mr-auto">
            <NavList />
          </Nav>
        </Navbar>
      </>)
}
export default NavigationBar
